# m1_wall_clear.shot — try to land on top of the mid-map wall column.
#
# The wall is at col 55 (x=1760-1792), 5 tiles tall (top at y=992,
# floor at y=1152). With air control 35% (98 px/s lateral) and jet
# thrust 2200 px/s², we *should* be able to jet up over it if we time
# the jet to start near the wall and hold right.

window 1280 720
seed   1 1
out    build/shots/wallclear
aim    2400 700

at  10 shot stand_t010
at  30 press right
burst run from 60 to 280 every 40

# Approach the wall — by tick 280 player is at x~1640 on the floor.
# Jet just before contact and hold right through the climb + arc.
at 280 press jet
burst lift from 285 to 360 every 5
at 360 release jet
burst arc from 365 to 440 every 10

# Check landing.
burst land from 450 to 540 every 15

at 560 end
